  "extract": "The Ecuador national football team, nicknamed La Tricolor, represents Ecuador in men's international football and is controlled by the Federación Ecuatoriana de Fútbol. They joined FIFA in 1926 and CONMEBOL a year later.",
  "extract_html": "<p>The <b>Ecuador national football team</b>, nicknamed <i><b>La Tricolor</b></i>, represents Ecuador in men's international football and is controlled by the Federación Ecuatoriana de Fútbol. They joined FIFA in 1926 and CONMEBOL a year later.</p>"
